# AutoDoc Local Rules

## Folder Structure

### Source Folders (in AutoDoc/)

```
DevTools/LegacyCodeTools/AutoDoc/
├── _css/                           # CSS stylesheets
│   ├── autodoc-shared.css          # Main shared styles
│   └── css-override.css            # Theme overrides
├── _images/                        # Image assets
│   ├── dedge.svg                      # FK logo (SVG)
│   └── dedge.ico                      # Favicon (ICO)
├── _js/                            # JavaScript files
│   ├── autodoc-diagram-controls.js # Diagram pan/zoom/fullscreen
│   ├── autodoc-mermaid-config.js   # Mermaid initialization & themes
│   └── svg-pan-zoom.js             # Pan-zoom library
├── _json/                          # Parser output data
├── _templates/                     # HTML templates
├── AutoDocBatchRunner.ps1          # Main generation script
├── Test-AutoDocGeneration.ps1      # Test wrapper script
└── _deploy.ps1                     # Deployment script
```

### Output Folder Structure

```
$env:OptPath\Webs\AutoDoc\
├── _css/, _images/, _js/           # Copied from source
├── _json/                          # Parser results
├── _templates/                     # Copied from source
├── index.html, web.config          # Copied from _templates/
└── *.html                          # Generated documentation files
```

### Folder Naming Convention

**All asset folders use underscore prefix (`_`) instead of dot (`.`):**
- This ensures IIS serves static files without hidden segment filtering issues
- Folders starting with `.` are blocked by IIS by default

### Folder Behavior During CleanRegenerate

**PRESERVED (never deleted):**
- `_css/`, `_js/`, `_images/` folders
- `index.html`, `web.config`

**CLEARED (content deleted, folder preserved):**
- `_json/` folder content (parser results regenerated)

## Template Placeholder Reference

| Placeholder | Replacement | Purpose |
|-------------|-------------|---------|
| `[controlsscripturl]` | `./_js/autodoc-diagram-controls.js?v={timestamp}` | Diagram controls |
| `[mermaidconfigurl]` | `./_js/autodoc-mermaid-config.js?v={timestamp}` | Mermaid config |
| `[imageurl]` | `./_images/dedge.svg` | FK logo |
| `[iconurl]` | `./_images/dedge.ico` | Favicon |
| `[css]` | Contents of `_css/autodoc-shared.css` | Inline styles |

**Note:** JS URLs include cache-busting timestamps (`?v=yyyyMMddHHmm`).

## AutoDocBatchRunner Parameters

| Parameter | Default | Description |
|-----------|---------|-------------|
| `$Regenerate` | `"std"` | Mode: `std`, `all`, `err`, `json`, `single` |
| `$SingleFile` | `""` | File path for `-Regenerate single` mode |
| `$CleanRegenerate` | `$true` | Full reset |
| `$MaxFilesPerType` | `0` | Limit files per type (0 = unlimited) |
| `$ClientSideRender` | `$true` | Use Mermaid.js in browser |
| `$UseRamDisk` | `$false` | Use RAM disk (V:) for work files |
| `$RamDiskSizeGB` | `4` | Size of RAM disk in GB |

**Regeneration Modes:**
- `std` - Only files changed since last run (default)
- `all` - Regenerate everything
- `err` - Only files with previous errors
- `json` - Only regenerate JSON index files
- `single` - Process only `$SingleFile`

## Testing

```powershell
# Test all file types from start
.\Test-AutoDocGeneration.ps1 -StartFromIndex 0

# Resume from specific index
.\Test-AutoDocGeneration.ps1 -StartFromIndex 2
```

## Troubleshooting

**Mermaid not rendering:**
- Ensure `<pre class="mermaid">` tags are used
- Check Mermaid CDN is accessible
- Check for "Maximum text size exceeded" → increase `maxTextSize`

**Text invisible in diagrams:**
- Mermaid 11 bug: foreignObject has 0x0 dimensions
- Fix: `fixForeignObjectDimensions()` runs on page load

**Dark mode lines not visible:**
- Ensure `autodoc-mermaid-config.js` is loaded
- Check `applyDarkModeLineStyles()` is being called
